result.execSummary:
The defendant Shavoni Marvell Williams Sr was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Shavoni Marvell Williams Sr is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Shavoni Marvell Williams Sr was found guilty of Intimidate Victim/Dissuade Complaints [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse, Repeater], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.44(2).
